. Naming convention:
    _Static: s_var
    _Global: g_var
    _Volatile: v_var
    _Function: This_func

. Project convention:
    _Split interrupt into separate file
    _Keep main as lightweight as possible
    _Group files into folder
      
.Git usage:
    _Pull rebase from master before pushing
    _Commit frequently (after 2 or 3 edit)
    _Switch branch for new feature
    _Rebase and solve conflict in own branch before merging
    _Master branch must always works
    _Delete branch after merging
